              "UUID": "0",
              "Value": "(L:last_lock) (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK, bool) != if{ (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK, bool) d (>L:last_lock) if{ (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR,feet) (A:INDICATED ALTITUDE, feet) - abs (A:VERTICAL SPEED, feet/minute) 0.20 * abs < if{ (A:AUTOPILOT ALTITUDE LOCK VAR, feet) } els{ (A:INDICATED ALTITUDE, feet) } } d (>L:cap_alt) } (L:cap_alt)",
